imdb.plot outline: We kick off our show with a little Halloween history and a lot of Woo Woo! Astrology Woo Woo that is. So much is happening in the Universe right now. The Sun, Mercury, Saturn and North Node in are all in the sign of Scorpio. Neptune is opposing Mars - those could be fighting words - but they are in signs Pisces and Virgo so it's far more constructive! And it is all part of a T-Square pointing at Pluto, so yeah, it's a doozy of a week. Plus we do a quick run down of how all these aspects and transits are manifesting in the media. Then Lauren finally breaks down for Jenn why the Wicked Witch of the West has tormented her for her entire life. Something about Neptune and Mercury/Pluto conjunction.
